{"type":"message","id":"2b84095f","parentId":"bd8adc63","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:53:52.645Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_8JrkOe71fc68XZdHIsOf0271","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw status\n\nOverview\n+----------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Item                 | Value                                                                                         |\n+----------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| OS                   | windows 10.0.22631 (x64) · node 24.15.0                                                       |\n| Dashboard            | http://127.0.0.1:18789/                                                                       |\n| Tailscale exposure   | off                                                                                           |\n| Channel              | stable (default)                                                                              |\n| Update               | pnpm · up to date · npm latest 2026.5.7                                                       |\n| Gateway              | local · ws://127.0.0.1:18789 (local loopback) · reachable 294ms · auth token · zt-c600365     |\n|                      | (192.168.93.59) app 2026.5.7 windows 10.0.22631                                               |\n| Gateway self         | zt-c600365 (192.168.93.59) app 2026.5.7 windows 10.0.22631                                    |\n| Gateway service      | Scheduled Task installed · registered · running (pid 17900, Verified gateway listener         |\n|                      | detected on port 18789 even though schtasks did not report a running task.)                   |\n| Node service         | Scheduled Task not installed                                                                  |\n| Agents               | 1 · no bootstrap files · sessions 7 · default main active just now                            |\n| Memory               | enabled (plugin memory-core) · not checked                                                    |\n| Plugin compatibility | none                                                                                          |\n| Probes               | enabled                                                                                       |\n| Events               | none                                                                                          |\n| Tasks                | 1 active · 0 queued · 1 running · no issues · audit clean · 5 tracked                         |\n| Heartbeat            | 30m (main)                                                                                    |\n| Last heartbeat       | none                                                                                          |\n| Sessions             | 7 active · default deepseek-v4-flash (1000k ctx) · ~\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\sessions. |\n|                      | json                                                                                          |\n+----------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n\nSecurity audit\nSummary: 3 critical · 6 warn · 1 info\n  CRITICAL Open groupPolicy with elevated tools enabled\n    Found groupPolicy=\"open\" at: - channels.feishu.groupPolicy With tools.elevated enabled, a prompt injection in those rooms can become a high-impact incident.\n    Fix: Set groupPolicy=\"allowlist\" and keep elevated allowlists extremely tight.\n  CRITICAL Open groupPolicy with runtime/filesystem tools exposed\n    Found groupPolicy=\"open\" at: - channels.feishu.groupPolicy Risky tool exposure contexts: - agents.defaults (sandbox=off; runtime=[exec, process]; fs=[read, wri…\n    Fix: For open groups, prefer tools.profile=\"messaging\" (or deny group:runtime/group:fs), set tools.fs.workspaceOnly=true, and use agents.defaults.sandbox.mode=\"all\" for exposed agents.\n  CRITICAL Feishu security warning\n    Feishu[default] groups: groupPolicy=\"open\" allows any member to trigger (mention-gated). Set channels.feishu.groupPolicy=\"allowlist\" + channels.feishu.groupAll…\n  WARN Reverse proxy headers are not trusted\n    gateway.bind is loopback and gateway.trustedProxies is empty. If you expose the Control UI through a reverse proxy, configure trusted proxies so local-client c…\n    Fix: Set gateway.trustedProxies to your proxy IPs or keep the Control UI local-only.\n  WARN Control UI insecure auth toggle enabled\n    gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth=true does not bypass secure context or device identity checks; only dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth disables Control UI device…\n    Fix: Disable it or switch to HTTPS (Tailscale Serve) or localhost.\n  WARN Insecure or dangerous config flags enabled\n    Detected 1 enabled flag(s): gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth=true.\n    Fix: Disable these flags when not actively debugging, or keep deployment scoped to trusted/local-only networks.\n… +3 more\nFull report: openclaw security audit\nDeep probe: openclaw security audit --deep\n\nChannels\n+----------+---------+--------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Channel  | Enabled | State  | Detail                                                                                 |\n+----------+---------+--------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Feishu   | ON      | OK     | configured                                                                             |\n+----------+---------+--------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n\nSessions\n+---------------------+--------+----------+-------------------+---------------------+----------------------------------+\n| Key                 | Kind   | Age      | Model             | Runtime             | Tokens                           |\n+---------------------+--------+----------+-------------------+---------------------+----------------------------------+\n| agent:main:main     | direct | just now | deepseek-v4-flash | OpenClaw Pi Default | 17k/1000k (2%) · 🗄️ 15% cached   |\n| agent:main:feishu:d | direct | 1m ago   | deepseek-v4-flash | OpenClaw Pi Default | 186k/1000k (19%) · 🗄️ 99% cached |\n| irect:ou_650…       |        |          |                   |                     |                                  |\n| agent:main:feishu:g | group  | 14m ago  | deepseek-v4-flash | OpenClaw Pi Default | 97k/1000k (10%) · 🗄️ 50% cached  |\n| roup:oc_59af…       |        |          |                   |                     |                                  |\n| agent:main:subagent | direct | 3h ago   | deepseek-v4-flash | OpenClaw Pi Default | 54k/1000k (5%) · 🗄️ 96% cached   |\n| :da4506ed-cf…       |        |          |                   |                     |                                  |\n| agent:main:feishu:g | group  | 4h ago   | deepseek-v4-flash | OpenClaw Pi Default | 53k/1000k (5%) · 🗄️ 53% cached   |\n| roup:oc_6fbb…       |        |          |                   |                     |                                  |\n| agent:main:subagent | direct | 5h ago   | deepseek-v4-flash | OpenClaw Pi Default | 45k/1000k (5%) · 🗄️ 94% cached   |\n| :66a90b78-2c…       |        |          |                   |                     |                                  |\n| agent:main:feishu:d | direct | 9h ago   | deepseek-v4-flash | OpenClaw Pi Default | unknown/1000k (?%)               |\n| irect:oc_6fb…       |        |          |                   |                     |                                  |\n+---------------------+--------+----------+-------------------+---------------------+----------------------------------+\n\nHealth\n+------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Item       | Status    | Detail                                                                                      |\n+------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Gateway    | reachable | 253ms                                                                                       |\n| Event loop | WARN      | reasons event_loop_utilization · max 0ms · p99 0ms · util 1 · cpu 0.507                     |\n| Feishu     | OK        | configured                                                                                  |\n+------------+-----------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n\nFAQ: https://docs.openclaw.ai/faq\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting\nNext steps:\n  Need to share?      openclaw status --all\n  Need to debug live? openclaw logs --follow\n  Need to test channels? openclaw status --deep\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","sessionId","exitCode","aggregated","name"],"status":"completed","sessionId":"crisp-wharf","name":"openclaw status","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778669632645}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a125e41","parentId":"2b84095f","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:54:00.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me summarize the findings for the user:\n\n1. **Core status**: ✅ Gateway running, Feishu connected, sessions active, no fatal errors\n2. **Security issues**: 🔴 3 critical items found:\n   - Feishu group policy is \"open\" with elevated tools enabled - prompt injection risk\n   - Open group policy with runtime/filesystem tools exposed\n   - Feishu security warning about open groups\n3. **Event loop delays**: ⚠️ There are liveness warnings about event loop delays (max ~5.7s). This seems to happen during startup/warmup phases. The current utilization is high (1.0 recently based on health check) but that might be transient.\n4. **Config warnings**: \n   - `plugins.allow` is empty (feishu plugin auto-loads)\n   - `gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth=true` is enabled\n   - Reverse proxy headers not trusted (not relevant for loopback)\n\nThe critical security issues are about Feishu group policy being set to \"open\" which means anyone in Feishu groups can potentially trigger the agent with elevated tools. This is the most important finding to report.\n\nLet me present this in a clean format.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"检查完毕，汇报一下结果：\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 整体状态 — 正常运行\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| Gateway | ✅ 运行中 (pid 17900) |\n| Feishu 通道 | ✅ WebSocket 已连接 |\n| 会话数 | 7 个活跃 |\n| Tasks | ✅ 1 个运行中，无异常 |\n| 版本 | 2026.5.7（最新） |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 发现的问题\n\n### 🔴 安全 — 3 个 CRITICAL（建议处理）\n\n1. **飞书群组策略为 `open` + 允许高权限工具**\n   - 任何在飞书群里的人都能触发 agent，且有 elevated 工具权限\n   - 如果群里混入恶意消息，存在 prompt injection 风险\n   - **建议:** 将 `channels.feishu.groupPolicy` 设为 `allowlist`，严格控制白名单群\n\n2. **群组开放了 runtime/filesystem 工具**\n   - 飞书群成员能通过 agent 执行命令和读写文件\n   - **建议:** 对群组用 `tools.profile=\"messaging\"` 或限制 runtime/fs 权限\n\n3. **Feishu 安全警告**\n   - 同上，群组策略过于宽松\n\n### 🟡 配置警告\n\n| 问题 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `allowInsecureAuth=true` | Control UI 不安全认证已开启 |\n| `plugins.allow` 未配置 | Feishu 插件自动加载中，建议显式设置信任列表 |\n\n### 🟡 Event Loop 延迟（消耗型，非错误）\n\n日志中出现了几次 `liveness warning: event_loop_delay`：\n- 最大延迟峰值 ~5.7s\n- 发生在启动阶段（model-prewarm, session-locks 等 sidecar 初始化时）\n- **不算 bug**，Windows 上 Node.js 的事件循环在启动加载期间被阻塞是正常的，服务稳定后恢复正常水平 ✅\n\n---\n\n**要不要我现在帮你修复这几个安全问题？** 主要是把飞书群策略改成 allowlist，防止群成员越权。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1802,"output":727,"cacheRead":42240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44769,"cost":{"input":0.00025228,"output":0.00020356,"cacheRead":0.00118272,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016385599999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778669632646,"responseId":"a74b5ed2-b082-40c9-a013-ccf97028c5cb"}}
