{"type":"message","id":"ee30cb40","parentId":"6a539bc7","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:56:34.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a batch file on the desktop that runs OpenClaw's gateway with admin privileges. Let me find the current gateway command and create a .bat file.\n\nFrom the earlier status output, I saw:\n- Command: `C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\dist\\index.js gateway --port 18789`\n- Service file: `~\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd`\n\nLet me check if the gateway.cmd already exists for reference.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_4Eku3iCAigcASpO4yOiF9805","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"type \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\gateway.cmd\" 2>&1","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":32355,"output":204,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34095,"cost":{"input":0.0045297,"output":0.00005712,"cacheRead":0.000043008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004629828}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778669791226,"responseId":"15e025ea-113e-4952-9cfd-ee53157978cc"}}
