{"type":"message","id":"9d280998","parentId":"aaf6b6a0","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:56:37.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to create a bat on the desktop that runs this with admin privileges. The standard way to request admin in a .bat file is to use `runas` or the PowerShell elevation method. The best approach for a double-clickable bat is to include an elevation check and relaunch with admin rights.\n\nLet me create a .bat file on the desktop.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_dZow2a0HNumyP3tJz4gq3238","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Desktop\\启动OpenClaw Gateway.bat","content":"@echo off\ntitle OpenClaw Gateway (管理员)\ncd /d \"%~dp0\"\n\n:: 检查管理员权限\nnet session >nul 2>&1\nif %errorLevel% neq 0 (\n    echo 正在请求管理员权限...\n    :: 以管理员身份重新启动自身\n    powershell -Command \"Start-Process '%~f0' -Verb RunAs\"\n    exit /b\n)\n\necho \u001b[32m[OK] 已获取管理员权限\u001b[0m\necho.\necho 正在启动 OpenClaw Gateway ...\n\nset \"OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789\"\n\"C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe\" C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\dist\\index.js gateway --port 18789\n\necho.\npause\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":254,"output":331,"cacheRead":34048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34633,"cost":{"input":0.000035560000000000005,"output":0.00009268,"cacheRead":0.000953344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001081584}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778669794536,"responseId":"4ded3e45-dbd2-4cf8-8f58-ee3b156b21c5"}}
