{"type":"message","id":"65e042bb","parentId":"2ef00ef2","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:52:59.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Unity executable exists. But there are two directories: `2020.3.49f1` and `2020.3.49f1-x86_64`. The path used is `2020.3.49f1` which exists.\n\nThe `spawn UNKNOWN` error in Node.js on Windows is typically a low-level OS error. Common causes:\n1. The executable path contains spaces - but it's properly quoted\n2. Windows is blocking the process creation (antivirus, etc.)\n3. Command line too long\n4. Some issue with how `powershell -Command` passes the arguments\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the error message: \"spawn failed\" with reason \"spawn UNKNOWN\". This is a Node.js `child_process.spawn` error that typically maps to Windows error code. \"UNKNOWN\" (EUNKNOWN) on Windows usually means error code 0 or an unknown system error.\n\nLet me look at TOOLS.md - there's a section about \"更新测试服\" that says:\n\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\tools\\hotupdate-scripts\\UpdateTestServer.ps1\"\n```\n\nBut the error shows it was trying to run a PowerShell inline script with `$unityPath`, `$projectPath`, etc. The `spawn UNKNOWN` is likely because the sub-agent was trying to execute this as a raw command via exec, but the command was too complex or had encoding issues.\n\nLet me check how the sub-agent was spawned and what it was actually trying to do. Also let me check if the actual batch file works correctly.\n\nActually, the key insight is: the command was sent as `raw_params` to `exec` with `timeout=30`. The `spawn UNKNOWN` error in Node.js child_process on Windows can happen when:\n1. The executable path has issues\n2. Windows API returns an unknown error code\n\nBut looking at the command more carefully - it's using `PowerShell Start-Process -NoNewWindow`. The `-NoNewWindow` flag might cause issues when spawning from Node.js. Let me try running the batch file directly instead, as documented in TOOLS.md.\n\nLet me also try to just run the Unity.exe directly to make sure it works.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Unity 存在。让我试试直接用 bat 跑，看看是不是命令格式问题。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_tCKajncDCQ09bdEa5VKz2131","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Test-Path \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\"","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_Mk7MwovoB4FKSRMRAI357652","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"& \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\" --version 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":157,"output":666,"cacheRead":39936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40759,"cost":{"input":0.000021980000000000003,"output":0.00018648000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0011182079999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013266679999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778673172829,"responseId":"cbf0c6e6-b64c-400a-8ccb-d4fd8331a89e"}}
