{"type":"message","id":"6f6ff083","parentId":"4b3e28b1","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:53:26.681Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_fCczFgYJ4S92NBNJ8zXS6177","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@echo off\r\nchcp 65001 >nul 2>&1\r\nsetlocal\r\n\r\n:: 涓?PlatformSwitcher.bat 涓€鑷达細鎸夋湰鏈哄畨瑁呬慨鏀?Unity 璺緞\r\nset \"UNITY_PATH=C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"\r\n\r\ncd /d \"%~dp0\" || exit /b 1\r\nset \"PROJECT_PATH=%CD%\"\r\nset \"LOG_FILE=%PROJECT_PATH%\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\r\n\r\nif not exist \"%UNITY_PATH%\" (\r\n    echo [ERROR] 鏈壘鍒?Unity.exe锛岃缂栬緫鏈?bat 涓殑 UNITY_PATH銆?\r\n    exit /b 1\r\n)\r\n\r\necho [INFO] projectPath=%PROJECT_PATH%\r\necho [INFO] 鎵ц鏃犲弬 RunHotUpdatePipeline锛氭祦姘寸嚎銆岀儹鏇淬€嶇殑鍏ㄩ儴鏈夋晥姝ラ\r\necho [INFO] log=%LOG_FILE%\r\n\r\n\"%UNITY_PATH%\" -batchmode -quit -nographics -projectPath \"%PROJECT_PATH%\" -executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline -logFile \"%LOG_FILE%\"\r\n\r\necho [INFO] Unity 閫€鍑虹爜: %ERRORLEVEL%\r\nexit /b %ERRORLEVEL%"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":228,"aggregated":"@echo off\r\nchcp 65001 >nul 2>&1\r\nsetlocal\r\n\r\n:: 涓?PlatformSwitcher.bat 涓€鑷达細鎸夋湰鏈哄畨瑁呬慨鏀?Unity 璺緞\r\nset \"UNITY_PATH=C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"\r\n\r\ncd /d \"%~dp0\" || exit /b 1\r\nset \"PROJECT_PATH=%CD%\"\r\nset \"LOG_FILE=%PROJECT_PATH%\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\r\n\r\nif not exist \"%UNITY_PATH%\" (\r\n    echo [ERROR] 鏈壘鍒?Unity.exe锛岃缂栬緫鏈?bat 涓殑 UNITY_PATH銆?\r\n    exit /b 1\r\n)\r\n\r\necho [INFO] projectPath=%PROJECT_PATH%\r\necho [INFO] 鎵ц鏃犲弬 RunHotUpdatePipeline锛氭祦姘寸嚎銆岀儹鏇淬€嶇殑鍏ㄩ儴鏈夋晥姝ラ\r\necho [INFO] log=%LOG_FILE%\r\n\r\n\"%UNITY_PATH%\" -batchmode -quit -nographics -projectPath \"%PROJECT_PATH%\" -executeMethod YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline -logFile \"%LOG_FILE%\"\r\n\r\necho [INFO] Unity 閫€鍑虹爜: %ERRORLEVEL%\r\nexit /b %ERRORLEVEL%","cwd":"C:\