{"type":"message","id":"4103ea7c","parentId":"100b9381","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:53:45.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the bat file works - it found Unity and tried to run it. The error \"Another Unity instance is running with this project\" means Unity Editor was open at the time. That's a separate issue from the `spawn UNKNOWN` error.\n\nSo the `spawn UNKNOWN` error was specifically a problem with how the sub-agent was trying to invoke the command. The bat file approach works fine (given Unity isn't already open).\n\nNow let me explain to the user:\n1. `spawn UNKNOWN` = Windows 底层进程创建失败，因为在 sub-agent 里直接传了一长串多行 PowerShell 内联脚本给 exec\n2. 正确的做法是用 bat 文件直接跑\n3. 刚才测试 bat 是能用的，只是 Unity Editor 还开着所以冲突了\n\nI should also update the TOOLS.md to make sure the sub-agents use the bat file approach instead of constructing inline PowerShell commands.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**问题原因搞清楚了：**\n\n`spawn UNKNOWN` 不是 Unity 的问题，而是 **sub-agent 调用 exec 时传了一整段多行 PowerShell 脚本内联执行**，Windows 底层进程创建接口处理这种长命令字符串时崩了，Node.js 返回了 UNKNOWN 错误。\n\n**用 bat 文件直接跑是正常的**（刚试了，找到了 Unity 路径，只是你 Unity Editor 还开着所以冲突了，关掉就能跑）。\n\n我更新一下 TOOLS.md，让 sub-agent 以后用 bat 而不是拼 PowerShell 脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_E4JA6rUSxUSZloPxqgA82047","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","offset":57,"limit":40}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":206,"output":411,"cacheRead":42880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43497,"cost":{"input":0.000028840000000000002,"output":0.00011508,"cacheRead":0.00120064,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00134456}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778673220444,"responseId":"c1a06e6e-f4ed-4e68-9012-35f0fce4585a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6ebd33b","parentId":"4103ea7c","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:53:45.481Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_E4JA6rUSxUSZloPxqgA82047","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n**更新完成后:** 在群里 @兵王(周以天) 通知更新完成。\n\n**实现方式:** 主 agent 只做快速操作（检查 + git pull），然后通过 sessions_spawn 创建 sub-agent 去跑 Unity 流水线。主 agent 立即释放，继续响应其他消息。sub-agent 在后台执行并监控日志，完成后自动汇报结果。\n\n**快捷命令:**\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\tools\\hotupdate-scripts\\UpdateTestServer.ps1\"\n```\n\n**手动执行 (bat):**\n`E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`\n\n**参数说明:**\n- Unity 路径: `C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Unity.exe`\n- 流水线入口: `YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline`\n- 流水线名称: \"热更\"（在 BuildPipeline 窗口配置）\n- CDN Git 根目录、渠道、版本等参数需在 Unity Editor 的 EditorConfig 中预先配置\n\n**注意:**\n- 首次使用需在 Unity Editor 中打开 BuildPipeline 窗口配置好 \"热更\" 流水线的各步骤参数\n- 运行需要管理员权限（Unity 许可证校验）\n- 完整的日志会输出到 `BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log`\n\n## Related\n\n- [Agent workspace](/concepts/agent-workspace)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778673225481}}
{"type":"message","id":"c708cb3e","parentId":"f6ebd33b","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:53:50.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that TOOLS.md has some instructions. The sub-agent was trying to run the Unity pipeline but used inline PowerShell. I need to update the instructions to make it clear that sub-agents should use the bat file directly, not construct PowerShell commands.\n\nLet me update the \"实现方式\" section to clarify the exec approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_pNcZV5Iqf0NSXEUff59A0451","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"**实现方式:** 主 agent 只做快速操作（检查 + git pull），然后通过 sessions_spawn 创建 sub-agent 去跑 Unity 流水线。主 agent 立即释放，继续响应其他消息。sub-agent 在后台执行并监控日志，完成后自动汇报结果。\n\n**快捷命令:**\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\tools\\hotupdate-scripts\\UpdateTestServer.ps1\"\n```\n\n**手动执行 (bat):**\n`E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`","newText":"**实现方式:** 主 agent 只做快速操作（检查 + git pull），然后通过 sessions_spawn 创建 sub-agent 去跑 Unity 流水线。主 agent 立即释放，继续响应其他消息。sub-agent 在后台执行并监控日志，完成后自动汇报结果。\n\n**⚠️ 重要：sub-agent 必须通过 bat 文件执行，不要拼内联 PowerShell 命令！**\n`spawn UNKNOWN` 是 Windows 底层创建进程失败的错误，多行内联 PowerShell 脚本通过 exec 直接传入会导致此问题。\n\n**正确写法 (sub-agent 内的 exec 命令):**\n```\n\"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\"\n```\n**无需包裹 cmd /c 或 powershell -Command**，exec 工具会直接启动 bat。\n\n**快捷命令 (手动执行):**\n```powershell\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\tools\\hotupdate-scripts\\UpdateTestServer.ps1\"\n```\n\n**手动执行 (bat):**\n`E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":452,"output":596,"cacheRead":43392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44440,"cost":{"input":0