{"type":"message","id":"9b546f0f","parentId":"a65136cc","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:53:53.667Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me summarize for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了，总结一下：\n\n---\n\n### `spawn UNKNOWN` 是什么\n\nWindows 底层进程创建失败。sub-agent 把一段多行 PowerShell 脚本直接塞给 exec，Node.js 的 `child_process.spawn` 解析不了这个命令，返回了操作系统层面的 UNKNOWN 错误。\n\n### 修复\n\n1. **已更新 TOOLS.md** — 明确要求 sub-agent 用 bat 文件执行，不再拼内联 PowerShell\n2. **bat 文件已验证可用** — 刚才跑了 bat，Unity 路径正确，只是你 Editor 开着所以冲突了（正常现象）\n3. **以后 sub-agent 执行 `\"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\"`** 就行，不需要任何包裹\n\n下次更新测试服的时候就不会再报这个了 ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":701,"output":192,"cacheRead":43776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44669,"cost":{"input":0.00009814,"output":0.00005376,"cacheRead":0.001225728,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013776279999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778673230369,"responseId":"4db5edcf-aec3-4666-8384-3b4d5de495f5"}}
